---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — B_AYAN" description="Heat & Flow Engineering researcher focused on CFD, rocket design, and eco-friendly HVAC systems.">
  <div class="max-w-2xl">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-8">About</h1>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        I'm a Heat & Flow Engineering researcher with a focus on computational fluid dynamics (CFD),
        rocket propulsion systems, and eco-friendly ventilation and HVAC design.
      </p>

      <h2>Research Interests</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Rocket design and propulsion systems</li>
        <li>Eco-friendly and sustainable HVAC solutions</li>
        <li>RANS turbulence modeling</li>
        <li>Computational Fluid Dynamics (CFD) simulations</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Tools & Methods</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>OpenFOAM, ANSYS Fluent</li>
        <li>Python, MATLAB for post-processing</li>
        <li>RANS, LES turbulence models</li>
        <li>Parametric CAD and mesh generation</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Reach me via <a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a> or
        explore my work on <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
